    Small utility to convert a the HYG CSV catalog to binary in the following format: - 32 bits (int) with the number of stars, starNum repeat the following starNum times (for each star) - 32 bits (int) - The the length of the name, or nameLength - 16 bits * nameLength (chars) - The name of the star - 32 bits (float) - appmag - 32 bits (float) - absmag - 32 bits (float) - colorbv - 32 bits (float) - ra - 32 bits (float) - dec - 32 bits (float) - distance
